      107.42,
      666.57,
      518.43,
      735.05
    ],
    "text": "On the morning of 11.07.2026, officers attached to the Walana Central Anti-Vice Unit, acting on a tip-off, conducted a raid in the Karadiyana area of the Piliyandala Police Division and arrested a suspect in possession of 78 litres and 750 millilitres of illicit liquor. The suspect was subsequently handed over to the Piliyandala Police Station for further legal action.",
